3.21	N844AA	N844AA	Ben Charles Padilla (born 1952) from Pensacola, Florida, a licensed aircraft mechanic, flight engineer, and pilot of small airplanes was aboard N844AA when it was stolen, and is believed by U.S. authorities to have been at the controls. He has not been seen or heard from since.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/bc/Ben.charles.arp.250pix.jpg/200px-Ben.charles.arp.250pix.jpg
